detailedDescription.articleBody:
Aline Nakashima is a Brazilian model discovered at a modeling competition at the age of 17. She has made two appearances in the Sports Illustrated Swimsuit Issue, in 2006 and 2007. Her modeling agency is Marilyn Agency, New York City.
Born in São José dos Campos, São Paulo, Brazil. Her father is Japanese-Brazilian and her mother is of Portuguese descent.
